<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Reset your password</title>
  <style>
    /* CÃ¡c style inline cho email */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f6f9fc;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4a90e2;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .reset-button {
      background-color: #4a90e2;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 16px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .reset-button:hover {
      background-color: #3d7bb6;
    }
    .fallback-link {
      word-break: break-all;
      color: #4a90e2;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>PASA Team</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi, {{name}}!</h2>
      <p>You recently requested to reset your password. Click the button below to proceed. This link is valid for a limited time.</p>
      <div class="button-container">
        <a class="reset-button" href="{{url}}" target="_blank">Reset Password</a>
      </div>
      <p>If the button above does not work, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:</p>
      <p class="fallback-link">{{url}}</p>
      <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support immediately.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you,<br/>PASA Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
